  <bodyText><![CDATA[<div class="g12">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<p><img src="/media/13070939/rome_donna_camilla_savelli_terrace.jpg" alt="Special occasion holidays in Italy" data-udi="umb://media/685c37bb31144e129e8dbe337014c8f2" /></p>
<h3>Get your glasses of bubbly ready to toast your holiday and celebrate your special occasion in Italy!</h3>
<p>From the romance of the <a data-udi="umb://document/201893063f65496384a9bd17846543a7" href="/{localLink:umb://document/201893063f65496384a9bd17846543a7}" title="Venice">Venice</a> waterways and the opera, combined with a blissful beach escape on a <a data-udi="umb://document/4265501ed34b4842883a8cfc5cd5cf1f" href="/{localLink:umb://document/4265501ed34b4842883a8cfc5cd5cf1f}" title="Italy Multi-Centre Holidays">multi-centre</a> honeymoon break; to a quick city break to <a data-udi="umb://document/17128dbb97a245cc842587a71ac17fa4" href="/{localLink:umb://document/17128dbb97a245cc842587a71ac17fa4}" title="Bologna">Bologna</a> to celebrate an anniversary – or a longer holiday with the whole <a data-udi="umb://document/7484af88886b4493a9304025f4744fc8" href="/{localLink:umb://document/7484af88886b4493a9304025f4744fc8}" title="Family Holidays in Italy">family</a> - we have the perfect dream trips. Tell us your ideas and we’ll find you a holiday you’ll cherish forever.</p>
</div>
<h3 align="center">Honeymoons in Italy</h3>
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<p><img src="/media/13070938/capri_view.jpg" alt="Honeymoons in Italy" data-udi="umb://media/4e76c8096c8c4faca71059634ef19191" /></p>
<p>You will love your honeymoon to Italy as there are so many exciting, dream trips to be experienced. You can enjoy an adventure in a city before relaxing on a heavenly beach on a multi-centre honeymoon. For example, combine seeing the stunning treasures of Florence with the sun-lit sands and hidden coves of the <a data-udi="umb://document/c0a1a2eb5f21493d858ec9013916a8fb" href="/{localLink:umb://document/c0a1a2eb5f21493d858ec9013916a8fb}" title="Liguria">Ligurian Riviera</a>, or the romance of Rome with the sublime coastline of <a data-udi="umb://document/1b38a4293ff04cc8b2dd360a57a538d8" href="/{localLink:umb://document/1b38a4293ff04cc8b2dd360a57a538d8}" title="Sorrento">Sorrento</a>.</p>
</div>
</div>
<h3 align="center">Celebratory City Breaks</h3>
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<p><img src="/media/13070940/milan_catherdral_.jpg" alt="Milan cathedral" data-udi="umb://media/cf51da799d8843178ba3e97b80ff1777" /></p>
<p>Whether you’re celebrating a milestone birthday or anniversary, or something else which means a lot, Italy offers an astonishing range of options for your special occasion. With its gastronomical pedigree, world-class historical sites, stunning architecture and artistic masterpieces you’re spoilt for choice. Why not go to a city you’ve never visited before? There’s <a data-udi="umb://document/2575554a5b50446eb00d5bf533f317cd" href="/{localLink:umb://document/2575554a5b50446eb00d5bf533f317cd}" title="Milan">Milan</a>, <a data-udi="umb://document/57bc5f34b7074843b7f19f3fc6cb7ac4" href="/{localLink:umb://document/57bc5f34b7074843b7f19f3fc6cb7ac4}" title="Rome">Rome</a>, <a data-udi="umb://document/8b79e45930f145f6b156a9152415fa9b" href="/{localLink:umb://document/8b79e45930f145f6b156a9152415fa9b}" title="Florence">Florence</a>, <a data-udi="umb://document/201893063f65496384a9bd17846543a7" href="/{localLink:umb://document/201893063f65496384a9bd17846543a7}" title="Venice">Venice</a>...</p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/b8b9c06b11684471be120fd623974058" href="/{localLink:umb://document/b8b9c06b11684471be120fd623974058}" title="Italy City Breaks"><strong>Find out more &gt;</strong></a></p>
</div>
<h3 align="center">Family Celebrations in Italy</h3>
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<p><img src="/media/13070941/umbria_assisi.jpg" alt="Family Celebrations in Italy" data-udi="umb://media/016ae4ed11564c279f0ed5a72d3c794e" /></p>
<p>Celebrate with your whole family on a trip of a lifetime to an Italian idyll. The Italian Lakes with their diverse landscapes offer something for every taste and desire. Its mild climate is perfect for gentle strolls by <a data-udi="umb://document/7d421e04a79044babf8cafda30e31d4a" href="/{localLink:umb://document/7d421e04a79044babf8cafda30e31d4a}" title="Lake Como">Lake Como</a>, <a data-udi="umb://document/ae52b40037474a3eadb1c0692c464473" href="/{localLink:umb://document/ae52b40037474a3eadb1c0692c464473}" title="Lake Garda">Garda</a> or <a data-udi="umb://document/476c8caf3fe84faab565f2d0f2e99f48" href="/{localLink:umb://document/476c8caf3fe84faab565f2d0f2e99f48}" title="Lake Maggiore">Maggiore</a>, or for boat trips across to exquisite islands. Stroll along cobbled streets to have a Cappuccino in a storybook village or admire stunning ornate waterside villas, well-preserved frescoes and immaculate Italianate gardens The more adventurous could enjoy swimming, some watersports or hiking up the verdant hillside paths amid olive groves and pines.<br /><br />Or perhaps enjoy a family holiday in the sparkling sandy seaside resorts of <a data-udi="umb://document/b037a20c14a3421ba33b32859c9e3344" href="/{localLink:umb://document/b037a20c14a3421ba33b32859c9e3344}" title="Sicily">Sicily</a> or a <a data-udi="umb://document/64b482b7dd774c0e9dd546e3c0c73e38" href="/{localLink:umb://document/64b482b7dd774c0e9dd546e3c0c73e38}" title="Italy Rural Country Holidays">rural retreat</a> in an agriturismo or masseria in beautiful <a data-udi="umb://document/d0c28188245b40a396dd64fb346dffcd" href="/{localLink:umb://document/d0c28188245b40a396dd64fb346dffcd}" title="Puglia">Puglia</a>. These authentic farm dwellings in the Italian countryside often have gardens and pools, as well as being handy for gentle walks and near to top-class attractions. They’re perfect for doing as much – or as little – as you like.</p>
</div>
